**Romance**, in the context of a cause, refers to the problem of
finding good ways to match people with others who are romantically
compatible. It also refers to the more general problem of helping
people enter and stay in happy romantic relationships.

# What is the problem?

- Current means of finding romantic partners seem astoundingly inefficient.[^pua]
Even online dating sites like OKCupid probably have low-hanging fruit for improvement.

- Many people seem profoundly unhappy even when they are in a relationship/married.
